'''Confluence''' 是一款建基於網路企業[[維基|維基]] (collaboration software) 的軟體，由澳洲軟體公司艾特萊森[[Atlassian|Atlassian]]所開發，<ref>{{cite book | author1=Krishna Sankar | author2=Susan A. Bouchard | title=Enterprise Web 2.0 Fundamentals | url=https://archive.org/details/enterpriseweb20f0000sank | date=24 April 2009 | publisher=Cisco Press | isbn=978-1-58705-763-2 | page=[https://archive.org/details/enterpriseweb20f0000sank/page/47 47]}}<!--|access-date=25 March 2012--></ref> 使用[[Java|Java]]編寫，並於2004年推出。Confluence 獨立軟體內建Tomcat網頁瀏覽器與[[HSQLDB|hsql]]資料庫，同時也支援其他資料庫<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://confluence.atlassian.com/doc/configuring-a-datasource-connection-937166084.html |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2020-12-24 |archive-date=2020-11-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201102111131/https://confluence.atlassian.com/doc/configuring-a-datasource-connection-937166084.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

開發公司在市場上將Confluence定位為[[企業軟體|企業軟體]]，可做為公司內部使用軟體或於[[SaaS|SaaS]]或於[[亞馬遜雲端運算服務|AWS]]上使用<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://aws.amazon.com/quickstart/architecture/atlassian-standard-infrastructure/ |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2020-12-24 |archive-date=2020-10-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201030222445/https://aws.amazon.com/quickstart/architecture/atlassian-standard-infrastructure/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite book | author1=Anja Ebersbach | author2=Markus Glaser | author3=Richard Heigl | author4=Alexander Warta | title=Wiki: Web Collaboration | url=https://archive.org/details/wikikooperationi00eber_287 | year=2008 | publisher=Springer | isbn=978-3-540-35150-4 | pages=[https://archive.org/details/wikikooperationi00eber_287/page/n347 337]–349}}<!-- | accessdate=25 March 2012--></ref>。

==概要==
艾特萊森於2004年3月25日推出Confluence，旨在建構一款「根據企業知識管理系統要求而編寫的應用程式，同時在處理上保留[[維基|維基]]的特色—簡單而強大」<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.theserverside.com/news/thread.tss?thread_id=24701 |title=Atlassian releases new wiki: Confluence 1.0 |publisher=Theserverside.com |accessdate=2011-09-19 |archive-date=2017-05-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170503232019/http://www.theserverside.com/news/thread.tss?thread_id=24701 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

在最新版本中，Confluence已整合為[[群組軟體|群組軟體]]的一部分<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.kmworld.com/Articles/PrintArticle.aspx?ArticleID=57533 |archive-url=https://archive.today/20120907014746/http://www.kmworld.com/Articles/PrintArticle.aspx?ArticleID=57533 |dead-url=yes |archive-date=2012-09-07 |title=Wiki tools are not all the same |publisher=KMWorld.com |date=2009-10-28 |accessdate=2011-09-19 }}</ref>，可以搭配[[JIRA|JIRA]]或其他艾特萊森軟體產品，包括 Bamboo, Clover,Crowd, Crucible,和Fisheye 使用<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.atlassian.com/software/confluence/overview/jira-users|title=Integrate Jira and Confluence Wiki|website=Atlassian.com|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120513014509/https://www.atlassian.com/software/confluence/overview/jira-users|archive-date=2012-05-13|accessdate=2020-12-24|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

艾特萊森於2014年推出匯流數據中心（Confluence Data Center），使群集設定中的節點負載均衡，進而提升可用性。

==分析==
{{Update|time=2021-01-23|reason=This paragraph is a decade old and thus obsolete in the current tense -- especially in the field of software.|date=February 2018}} 2007年，《給傻瓜的社交媒體行銷》（Social Media Marketing for Dummies）一書將Confluence視為一款「新興的企業社交軟體」，且肯定Confluence已確實成為市場競爭者<ref>{{cite book |url=https://archive.org/details/socialmediamarke0000sing |title=Social Media Marketing For Dummies |page=
[https://archive.org/details/socialmediamarke0000sing/page/214 214] |first1=Shiv |last1=Singh |first2=Michael |last2=Becker |first3=Ryan |last3=Williams |publisher=[[John_Wiley_&_Sons|John Wiley & Sons]] |date=2009-09-26 |isbn=978-0-470-28934-1 }}</ref> 。《給傻瓜的維基》（Wiki for Dummies）則描述Confluence為「企業環境最流行的維基百科之一」、「安裝簡單、使用輕鬆」，以及擁有「突破框架」的Wiki軟體搜尋能力。''<ref>{{cite book |url=https://books.google.com/books?id=5VXgXlU7g-YC |title=Wikis for dummies |first1=Dan |last1=Woods |first2=Peter |last2=Thoeny |publisher=[[John_Wiley_&_Sons|John Wiley & Sons]] |page=[https://books.google.com/books?id=5VXgXlU7g-YC&pg=PA193 193] |date=2007-07-23 |isbn=978-0-470-04399-8 }}</ref>

{{link-en|eWeek}}在2011年引述了Confluence第4版的新功能，如：自動規格化與自動完成，並整合Wiki與[[所見即所得|WYSIWYG（所見即所得）]]，[[社交網絡|社交網絡]]通知以及多媒體文件的拖放功能<ref name="eWeek">{{cite web |url=http://www.eweek.com/c/a/Enterprise-Applications/Atlassian-Delivers-Confluence-4-603258/ |work=[[eWeek|eWeek]]|title=Atlassian Delivers Confluence 4 |first=Darryl K. |last=Taft |date=2011-09-19 |access-date=2012-03-24 }}</ref>。涵蓋基本的企業溝通、知識交流的協作工作區、社交網絡、[[個人資訊管理|個人資訊管理]]和[[專案管理|專案管理]]。來自[[國際數據集團|IDG國際數據集團]]的德國報社Confluence與[[SharePoint|SharePoint]]進行比較，發現 Confluence 非常適合作為社交業務的入門協作平台，而 SharePoint 更偏向業務流程具高複雜結構的公司<ref>{{cite web |language=de |url=http://www.computerwoche.de/software/office-collaboration/2507049/ |title=Sharepoint versus Confluence und Jive |first1=Jörg |last1=Schmidl  |first2=Johannes |last2=Reebs  |first3=Oliver |last3=Wucher amp |work=Computerwoche |date=2012-03-16 |accessdate=2012-03-24 |archive-date=2012-12-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121201043425/http://www.computerwoche.de/software/office-collaboration/2507049/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

Confluence 的功能包含為所有頁面（包含Word檔案）設置CSS模板。内建搜尋功能，可以用日期、網頁作者以及內容類型（如圖像）進行搜尋。工具中設置了附加功能，可整合標準格式，可編碼API使其具備擴充性。Confluence 可作為大綱工具，對應同軟體公司所開發的Jira—[[事務跟蹤管理系統|事務跟蹤管理系統]]中的工作需求<ref>{{cite web|url=http://blogs.atlassian.com/2013/12/confluence-5-4-jira-integrates-confluence-like-never-before/|title=Atlassian Blogs|accessdate=2020-12-24|archive-date=2016-03-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160323063254/https://blogs.atlassian.com/2013/12/confluence-5-4-jira-integrates-confluence-like-never-before/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

==停用Wiki標記式語言==
Confluence於2011年<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://confluence.atlassian.com/doc/confluence-4-0-release-notes-228622806.html |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2020-12-24 |archive-date=2020-11-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201113184547/https://confluence.atlassian.com/doc/confluence-4-0-release-notes-228622806.html |dead-url=no }}</ref> 停止支援[[wiki|Wiki 標記式語言]] <ref>{{cite web |author=Atlassian |url=https://confluence.atlassian.com/display/CONF40/Confluence+4+Editor+-+What%27s+Changed+for+Users+of+the+Old+Rich+Text+Editor |title=Confluence 4.0 Editor - What's Changed for Users of the Old Rich Text Editor |publisher=Atlassian.com |access-date=2018-03-28 |archive-date=2020-10-31 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201031141555/https://confluence.atlassian.com/display/CONF40/Confluence+4+Editor+-+What's+Changed+for+Users+of+the+Old+Rich+Text+Editor |dead-url=no }}</ref>。這項決定於日前被熱烈議論，上個版本的使用者中有部分反對此變更<ref>{{cite web |author=Atlassian |url=https://confluence.atlassian.com/display/CONF43/Confluence+4+Editor+-+Customer+Feedback |title=Confluence 4 Editor - Customer Feedback |publisher=Atlassian.com |accessdate=2013-04-16 |archive-date=2020-10-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201030214411/https://confluence.atlassian.com/display/CONF43/Confluence+4+Editor+-+Customer+Feedback |dead-url=no }}</ref> 。對此，艾特萊森提供[[外掛程式|外掛程式]]，進階使用者可利用原始碼編輯器，針對 XHTML 文件原始碼進行編輯<ref>{{cite web |author=Atlassian |url=http://confluence.atlassian.com/display/DOC/Specification+-+Confluence+Advanced+Editor |title=Specification - Confluence Advanced Editor |publisher=Atlassian.com |accessdate=2012-04-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120412131456/http://confluence.atlassian.com/display/DOC/Specification+-+Confluence+Advanced+Editor |archive-date=2012-04-12 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。但是，雖然新的標記式語言基於 XHTML 進行編寫，卻不完全適用 XHTML<ref>{{cite web|author=Atlassian|url=https://confluence.atlassian.com/display/DOC/Confluence+Storage+Format|title=Confluence Storage Format|publisher=Atlassian.com|accessdate=21 Mar 2014|quote=We refer to the Confluence storage format as 'XHTML-based'. To be correct, we should call it XML, because the Confluence storage format does not comply with the XHTML definition.|archive-date=2015-05-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150531162438/https://confluence.atlassian.com/display/DOC/Confluence+Storage+Format|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

此外，Wiki標記式語言不僅可鍵入編輯器，透過Confluence的自動完成及自動格式化功能，還可將Wiki標記式語言轉碼成新的格式<ref>{{cite web | last=Atlassian | title=Confluence 4.0 Editor - What's Changed for Wiki Markup Users | url=https://confluence.atlassian.com/display/CONF40/Confluence+4+Editor+-+What%27s+Changed+for+Wiki+Markup+Users | accessdate=2018-03-28 | archive-date=2020-11-13 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201113093025/https://confluence.atlassian.com/display/CONF40/Confluence+4+Editor+-+What%27s+Changed+for+Wiki+Markup+Users | dead-url=no }}</ref>。及時轉換完成後，將無法再次以 Wiki 標記式語言進行編寫。

== 安全性 ==
Confluence雲端資料庫的傳輸及保存均經過加密保護<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.atlassian.com/trust/security/security-practices?_ga=2.85233360.890195763.1562477558-1980951556.1561525377#faq-5fd9f2cf-d7c7-40fa-af1f-854e2d9f3f48 |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2020-12-24 |archive-date=2020-10-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201027183926/https://www.atlassian.com/trust/security/security-practices?_ga=2.85233360.890195763.1562477558-1980951556.1561525377#faq-5fd9f2cf-d7c7-40fa-af1f-854e2d9f3f48 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

